					h3 About Seven Albums
					p Seven Albums is an online platform for store remodeling and design, providing retail owners with the tools and products they need to outfit their stores.
					p We understand that shoppers are looking for more than just clothes when they enter a boutique. They come to your store for the entire experience.
					p.about Whether you are opening a new store or rehabbing a long-standing retail establishment, creating a unique and consistent image, mood and visual experience that reaches your customers can be a challenge.
